# Inciting Event (Choice)

the catalyst is the event that disrupts your protagonist’s status quo. But they’re not ready to make the choice that catapults them into the story just yet.

You are not in a problem transforming world.

Look back on your Life
Look at your family
Look at your friends
Look at your colleagues
Look at your community
Look at your country
Look at your world

Ask for each of these groups what drives your actions.

Using the premise that "Progress = People & Problems" ask what problems are driving progress in each of these groups.   

Remove the problems from your world. Ask what is left? What would get done?



